<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.4.7">
<l>cālappal niraippiṉṉē taḻaik kāviṉ</l>
<l rend="indent">kīḻtaṉti rumēṉiniṉ ṟoḷi tikaḻa</l>
<l>nīla nalnaṟuṅ kuñci nēttirat</l>
<l rend="indent">tālaṇin tupallāyar kuḻām naṭuvē</l>
<l>kōlaccen tāmaraik kaṇmi ḷirak</l>
<l rend="indent">kuḻalūti yicaipāṭik kuṉittā yarōṭā</l>
<l>littuva rukiṉṟa vāyap piḷḷai</l>
<l rend="indent">yaḻakukaṇ ṭeṉmaka ḷayarkkiṉ ṟatē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Behind the massive herd, beneath a forest of foliage,</l>
<l rend="indent">as his holy body continues to shine brightly,</l>
<l>[his] tuft of hair pleasantly fragrant with blue lotuses</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] adorned with peacock feathers,</l>
<l>in the midst of a group of many herders,</l>
<l rend="indent">playing [his] flute, singing songs,</l>
<l rend="indent">[and] dancing along with the herder [boys]</l>
<l>as [he] rolls [his] beautiful red lotus eyes,</l>
<l rend="indent">my daughter saw the beauty of the cowherd boy</l>
<l>who came [along] noisily [and] forgets [herself].</l> 
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
